name: Amiganitzu
overview: 30 levels of frustrating fun! Collect all the keys and then exit via the door. Spiders will kill you if you are caught adjacent to them. Spiders will explode if they can no longer move. Snakes will spit deadly poison if you are in their line of site. Be quick or the traps will get you, but they can be blocked with boulders. Collect gems for extra points and extra lives.
